name: Dogu Shepherd
description:
#03/07 of DOGU - White Series

One day, while munching on some odd-looking red plants and watching his herd of sheep, Dogu Shepherd had enlightenment.

From that moment he dedicated his life to spreading these words of wisdom:

"The sheep you should be herding are within you. Keep on chomping the red stuff."
- Dogu Shpeherd

---

The White Series focuses on combining old nature pictures with the DOGUs.

This series consists of 6 DOGUs and one secret DOGU.
